`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"IIIT Una operates in Una, Himachal Pradesh, giving interns access to regional industries and research ecosystems. The campus hosts active centers spanning AI/ML and data, Computer vision, Networks and communications and collaborates with government and industry sponsors. If you are comparing across top public tech institutes, anchor your choices with labs, facilities, and sponsored work rather than brand alone."}),`
`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"Because the institute is embedded in Una, interns can tap into nearby industry partners, field sites, and alumni-led startups. This often translates to problem statements with real datasets or hardware constraints rather than purely academic exercises."}),`
