`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"IIT Gandhinagar operates in Gandhinagar, Gujarat, giving interns access to regional industries and research ecosystems. The campus hosts active centers spanning Sustainable engineering, Robotics and intelligent systems, AI/ML and data and collaborates with government and industry sponsors. If you are comparing across the IIT system, anchor your choices with the IIT internships hub to see where this institute leads on depth, facilities, and sponsored work."}),`
`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"Because the institute is embedded in Gandhinagar, interns can tap into nearby industry partners, field sites, and alumni-led startups. This often translates to problem statements with real datasets or hardware constraints rather than purely academic exercises."}),`
